<button id="euc-play-btn">▶ PLAY</button>
<button class="gold" id="euc-randomize-btn">✦ RANDOMIZE</button>
</div>
<div class="edu-card">"The Euclidean algorithm generates traditional musical rhythms" — Godfried Toussaint, 2004. E(3,8) = [x..x..x.] = the Cuban tresillo. E(5,8) = the Cuban cinquillo. E(4,12) = the West African standard bell. These are not approximations — they are mathematically exact reproductions of world rhythm traditions.</div>
</section>
